\SE[37]Ugh... I'm sorry.... \SE[53]I couldn't put as much

\SE[44]Please be careful...? \!\SE[1]You went through all the
trouble of saving me, but if you slip in the bath and end up

\SE[24]Yes... Regarding that matter.... \SE[52]I am filled with

\SE[2]By the way, why is Tita-chan sitting all the way over

\SE[9]No...!! \.It's not like that...! \!\SE[23]Um, it's just

\SE[21]'Resolve,' huh... \!\SE[0]Hehe... Tita-chan, you're such a

\SE[54] (Somehow... it feels nostalgic. It's as if I'm looking at
my old self...)

\SE[56]...Come over here. \!\SE[55]If you make me wait too long,
Lunaroa will turn into a boiled octopus.

\SE\SE[45]You finally came. \!\SE[45]Tita-chan is quite shy,
isn't she?

\SE[52]I... was holding back for the sake of the two of you.
\SE[33]Laura likes Lunaroa-sama... \SE[38]And Lunaroa-sama...
feels the same way...

\SE[7]I thought that I couldn't interfere... \!\SE[53]...that's
what I thought.

\SE[2] Did you know that while Lunaroa-sama was sleeping...
\SE[3] A new bill was passed in Ulyssean?

\SE[2]So something like that happened. \SE[1]I wonder what kind
of bill it was?

\SE[5] (Because I've always been working so hard... \!\SE[0]I
also don't really understand that kind of talk...)

\SE[14]I don't know about that...! \SE[13]It's true that the laws
have changed in these past three years!

\SE[32] After taking care of her... I was thinking of distancing
myself from Lunaroa-sama. \SE[3] But, the awakened Lunaroa-sama
is beautiful and kind...

\SE[14] My 'innocence' has completely disappeared! I will no
longer suppress my feelings!! \SE[13]......\SE[14] Lunaroa-
sama!!!

\SE[12] I love Lunaroa-sama! \!\SE[13] Please marry me!!
\!\SE[14] I don't care what number I am, as long as I can be
close to you...!!

\SE[7]W-What should I do... Laura. \SE[59]This has become a
serious situation...!

\SE[65]Even if you ask me what should we do... \SE[24]I-I didn't
know there was such a law...

\SE[7] (I've caused trouble for Lunaroa-sama... \!\SE[38] Maybe,
I really am unworthy after all...)

It's the 'Yuri Branch'...! Let's choose the development after
this!

\SE[71] (Nevertheless, having a polygamous marriage is quite
something, even for a yuri scene...)

\SE[66]Even if it's considered legal, I wonder how I feel about
it...?
\SE[2]A match...? \!\SE[8]I can't fight or anything like that...?

\SE[13]Don't say that! The match is simple! \SE[16]From now on,
the one who makes Lunaroa happy with the two of us wins...!
\SE[12]...There shouldn't be any complaints about this, right?

\SE[14]How can I make Lunaroa-sama happy...!? \SE[13]What a
wonderful sound... But, how can I do that...?

\SE[15]It's okay...! \SE[13]I have a good magic for times like
this...!

\SE[14]With this, everything is ready...! \.From now on, I will
use this to make Luna happy! \!\SE[13]The one who can make her
the happiest wins...!

\SE[9]Even if you suddenly say that...! \!\SE[8]M-Me, do
something like that...!?
\SE[63]Is it okay to be so leisurely...?

\SE[57]Luna... From now on, I will make you happy, okay? \SE[55]I
will fill in the gap you have... \SE[62]It's been a while, so you
must be really pent up. \SE[61]Here... ♡

\SE[63]If things continue like this, will Luna become happy with
just me...? \SE[61]Is it okay for me to just watch from here...?

\SE[12]Just watching...? \!\SE[28]No...! \.I'm not that kind of
easy-to-understand girl...!!

\SE[12]Take a step forward with courage, Tita...!! \SE[13]I've
already stopped hesitating...! \SE[14]Even if I'm disliked by the
other person... I won't have any regrets...!

\SE[13]A woman needs courage...! \!\SE[14]Lady Lunaroa... Please
excuse me!!

\SE[34]I-I can't give in! This is something really important...!
\SE[30]I will make you happy by getting married!

\SE[13]......\.......\.......\!\SE[12]Is it really happiness for
Lady Lunaroa to marry Laura? \!\SE[14]Can you really prove that
it's true...!?

\SE[64]P-Prove it...!? \SE[70]Well... I definitely have the
determination to accomplish it, or rather, I'm very motivated!!

\SE[13]Didn't I say prove it? It's not just about feelings or
motivation. \SE[12]I need a guarantee that there's absolutely no
mistake.

\SE[2]For example, if Laura were to die in an accident, \SE[1]it
wouldn't matter how motivated or how much I feel, right? \SE[1]In
that case, Lady Lunaroa wouldn't be able to become happy, right?

\SE[65]E-Even if you say that, this is the only thing I can
do...!

\SE[2] (Oh my, this is the Devil's Proof, isn't it? \SE[15] Tita-
chan, you're quite eloquent...)

\SE[14] I will assert myself as the Second Consort!! \SE[13] I
demand the right to have a stand-in date every day!! I want to
establish a fixed turn for myself...!!

\SE[82]A Second Consort...!!? Asserting the right to have a
date!?

\SE[47]...I don't want to say this, but I have been taking care
of Lady Lunaroa for three years. \SE[48] Shouldn't I be granted
that kind of right?
\SE[70]Um, well...! \SE[47]How should I put it, um...!!

\SE[57] (She's quite formidable, Tita-chan. \SE[45] Laura is
being so nice to a younger girl... \SE[21] Sigh... How
adorable...)
